GVM tool - http://gvmtool.net/
install with -> curl -s get.gvmtool.net | bash
REQUIRES JAVA ALREADY INSTALLED AND $JAVA_HOME SETUP

install groovy -> gvm install groovy
install gradle -> gvm install gradle
install grails -> gvm install grails

Project Directory Structure
--------------------------
project_name/src/main/java
project_name/src/main/resources
project_name/src/main/groovy
project_name/test/java
project_name/test/resources
project_name/test/groovy
project_name/src/<sourceSet>/java
project_name/src/<sourceSet>/resources
project_name/src/<sourceSet>/groovy


